<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="17Dec1934"><font color="red">17 December 1934</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from J. Ralph Pinker to Paul L&eacute;on): John Lane have two copies of Ulysses &hellip; the Random House edition and the &hellip; Odyssey Press &hellip; glad to know which Mr Joyce would like them to follow and whether there are corrections to be made to either. </div>
